Claire Nebout https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Claire_Nebout 0 Claire Nebout (born 20 May 1964) is a French actress. She has appeared in 55 films and television shows since 1986. She co-starred in In the Country of Juliets, which was entered into the 1992 Cannes Film Festival. Claire_Nebout ( born_20_May_1964 ) is a_French_actress .
